data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom home located in an awesome part of Port Saint Lucie with easy access to 95/turnpike and Becker area!   New interior and exterior paint, Newer AC 2016, New Hot Water Heater 2022, Brand New flooring throughout, remodeled guest bathroom, Huge yard completely fenced in. Stainless steel appliances and new dishwasher in the kitchen, split floor plan, open layout. Vaulted ceilings in the main living area with access to the covered patio and huge backyard. Master suite has a walk in closet, custom shelving and barn door to the master bathroom. Come check out this beautiful home today! (Backyard Playset does not convey)
